data.description: Come make this Parkway Villages stunner your home! Swanky hardwoods in foyer lead to inviting living room w/ cozy fireplace. Tall ceilings throughout main level make this a top notch home! Fabulous kitchen includes granite counters, hardwood cabinets, modern tile flooring with bright recessed lighting & island. Look up in the master retreat to see a gorgeous trey ceiling! Look further and you'll find a master bath w/ dual vanity, separate tub & shower, & huge walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms have vaulted ceilings & spacious closets! With easy access to all highways, this is the place to be!
